# 🧠 AI Text Summarizer Web App

This is a simple full-stack web application that uses **OpenAI's GPT model** to generate concise summaries of long text. Users can input a large paragraph, and the app will return a short, meaningful summary powered by AI.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔤 Paste any long paragraph or article
- ✂️ Get a summarized version using GPT-3.5
- 🌐 Easy-to-use web interface
- ⚙️ Node.js backend connected to OpenAI API

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer     | Tech Used               |
|-----------|--------------------------|
| Frontend  | HTML, CSS, JavaScript    |
| Backend   | Node.js, Express         |
| LLM       | OpenAI GPT-3.5 via API   |

---

